                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Minister <persName type="to">Hicks</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <hi rend="italic">
                            <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-08-20">August 20, 1906</date>
                        </hi>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>President Roosevelt has cabled directly to President of Chile an expression of
                    intense sympathy felt at the appalling disaster that has befallen her. You will
                    supplement this by the proper representations at the foreign office.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
